	<div id="description">Galactic Pizza takes you on a journey to a galaxy not so far away.
	You play as an intergalactic pizza boy whose pizzas have been stolen by a band of hungry aliens. 
	Determined to make the delivery, he followed them.
	You must make your way through the aliens hideout and get the precious pizzas back.
	But be careful, these hideouts are filled with tricky puzzles and dangerous aliens.</div>
	
